{"tid":400923,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句,無論IPHONE8定8PLUS都會第一日就負數","createTime":"2017-09-15T08:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T11:57:12.000Z","uid":63113,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a50615263b9b0edbd355988f43473c32724664b4","tid":400923,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"真心問下自己呢兩部同上嗰代比係有咩大分別<br />\n<br />\n香港人買手機至緊要咪係要show到比人睇我有大撚把錢呀而家 換咗部靚靚新手機 <br />\n<br />\n仲要係新IPHoNE添！<br />\n<br />\n你自己而家睇下個樣 無論正面定背面<br />\n<br />\n假設你戴埋手機殻 真係問你點撚樣分得出7仔定8仔都難過鬼<br />\n<br />\n肯定負撚硬數<br />\n<br />\n下個月個乜鬼X連碌龍珠都打直擺就知蘋果挑通眼眉啦屌<br />\n<br />\n前面個額頭你拎出街街邊啲阿伯都會講聲靚仔咁識貨<br />\n<br />\n訂撚咗8嗰啲當無件事發生好過"},{"pid":"3919071fee18e03d548a1b29cdb958332ad96267","tid":400923,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6ec16ede083a43d9c50d9eb119a5955b710e01e","tid":400923,"uid":8302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你訂唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca0a059363fa533eeec2a1502727c8d13c45c4b","tid":400923,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"7b13052eaec241771b6923b9a86ff455df2fcd57","tid":400923,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你訂唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你 下個月先訂啦 呢部訂撚咗愛嚟炒真係比人笑"},{"pid":"f7565d1d6663d9c92878b104c8858fb4f4d055dd","tid":400923,"uid":5970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501c3762cabd1f301d56d4dd30061d8a8968b3a3","tid":400923,"uid":3302,"like":0,"disl